
-- Debugger PHP/Python --

per correggere errore:
	python module vim_debug not found...
installare vim-debug con python-pip
	sudo pip install dbgp vim-debug

documentazione: https://github.com/jaredly/vim-debug

-- pacchetti archlinux per plugin vim --

vim-cecutil 17-1 (vim-plugins)
	save/restore window position, mark position, selected user maps
vim-debug-git 20120110-1
	This plugin creates an integrated debugging environment in VIM.
vim-gundo 2.3.0-1 (vim-plugins)
	Vim plugin to visualize your Vim undo tree
vim-manpageview 24c-3 (vim-plugins)
	Viewer for manpages, gnu info, perldoc, and php (unix/linux/cygwin)
vim-sco 4.02-5 (vim-plugins)
	Browse source code easily with cscope, ctags and marks system
